表的代码预览取药员_3121005358欧炜标

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('collector') and o.name = 'FK_COLLECTO_MANAGEC_ADMIN')
alter table collector
drop constraint FK_COLLECTO_MANAGEC_ADMIN
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('collector')
and name = 'managec_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index collector.managec_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('collector')
and type = 'U')
drop table collector
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: collector */
/*==============================================================*/
create table collector (
cno char(8) not null,
ano char(8) null,
cname char(15) not null,
caccount char(20) not null,
cpassword char(20) not null,
constraint PK_COLLECTOR primary key nonclustered (cno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: managec_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index managec_FK on collector (
ano ASC
)
go

alter table collector
add constraint FK_COLLECTO_MANAGEC_ADMIN foreign key (ano)
references admin (ano)
go
